/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, providing a driver's eye view of the scene. The street is lined with lush green trees and bushes, adding a touch of nature to the urban landscape. Overhead, power lines crisscross against the backdrop of a cloudy sky, a common sight in many cityscapes. In the distance, a concrete overpass stretches across the scene, a testament to the city's infrastructure. The colors in the image are predominantly green and gray, reflecting the blend of natural and man-made elements.
